article.headline: Cal St.-Fullerton 80, UC Irvine 74
article.story: FULLERTON, Calif. -- Isiah Umipig scored 19 points, Orane Chin added 15 points and 12 rebounds and Cal State-Fullerton held off UC Irvine 80-74 Thursday night. Jer'Vaughn Johnson finished with 14 points for the Titans (9-14, 5-5 Big West). Perry Webster had 13 and Andre Hardy 12. Darren Moore led the Anteaters (10-13, 3-6) with 22 points, Mike Wilder scored 20 and Patrick Rembert 16, including four 3-pointers. Fullerton led by 14 in the first half and took a 38-28 advantage into intermission. The Titans outshot UC Irvine 52.9 percent to 39.3 percent, and their bench outscored the Anteaters' 21-9.
